Class CotImportExportHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.atakmap.android.importexport.handlers.CotImportExportHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MapEventDispatcher.MapEventDispatchListener, CotServiceRemote.ConnectionListener, CotServiceRemote.CotEventListener
    public class CotImportExportHandler
extends java.lang.Object
implements CotServiceRemote.ConnectionListener, CotServiceRemote.CotEventListener, MapEventDispatcher.MapEventDispatchListener
    Bridges the CoT event bus (events from StateSaver, CoT events coming in over the network, etc) with the import/export handlers managed by ImportExportComponent and ITEM_PERSIST MapEvents.
